      - uses: actions/checkout@v4
      - uses: actions/setup-python@v5
        with:
          python-version: '3.12'
      - run: pip install -r requirements.txt
      - run: pytest
```

Adapt for Go (`go test ./...`), Ruby (`bundle exec rake test`), Rust (`cargo test`), etc.

